            name="oliver liam"
            company="viking burrito"
            email="oliver@burrito.com"
            vat="FRB1235476"
          />

            name="lucas harper"
            company="stone tech zone"

            vat="FRB1235476"
          />

            name="ethan james"
            company="fiber notion"
            email="ethan@fiber.com"
            vat="FRB1235476"

export default BillingInformation;
